  "gloss": "The compiler's decidable rational representation of the dynamics agrees exactly with the real-valued semantics: a relation is a congruence over the reals precisely when it is one over the rationals. The executable carrier proves neither more nor less than the real theory.\n\n**Cites** `WMSpec.Compiler.dynCongQ_iff` — the corpus theorem this result restates and discharges.\n\n**Original contribution.** The corpus lemma is a bare iff; the thesis states it as a conservativity guarantee, that the executable rational carrier neither loses real facts nor invents ones the real semantics does not state.\n",
